# Editor → render-service URL. OPTIONAL override — usually leave this unset.
#
# By default the editor posts SAME-ORIGIN (/render):
#   - dev:  the Vite dev server proxies /render to the local sidecar you start
#           with `bun run render:server` (see vite.config.ts).
#   - prod: Caddy reverse-proxies /render to the sidecar (deploy/Caddyfile.example).
#
# Only set this to point the editor at a sidecar on a different origin (e.g. a
# remote render host or a non-default port that the dev proxy doesn't cover):
# VITE_VELLUM_RENDER_URL=http://localhost:5252
